HEADWORD: Aloud
<hw>A*loud"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>a-</ets> + <ets>loud</ets>.]</ety> <def>With a loud voice, or great
noise; loudly; audibly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Cry <qex>aloud</qex>, spare not, lift up thy voice.</q>
<rj><qau>Isa. lviii. 1.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

